        },
        {
          "text": "In my college this no proper placement for any graduation, there is no financial support for poor peoples",
          "name": "Bhuvan Kumar TM",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Voc"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no cultural activities in our college, no compulsory uniform, no transport facility, and worst method the use for payment for examination fees",
          "name": "Bhuvan Kumar TM",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Voc"
        },
        {
          "text": "This no proper maintenance of a ground for sports ,",
          "name": "Bhuvan Kumar TM",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Voc"
        },
        {
          "text": "No transport facility, no compulsory uniform system, no financial support for merit students and poor students,",
          "name": "Pramod AS",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Voc"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no other facilities for backward category students, there is no compulsory ID card for students and also professors",
